                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                        </p>
                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                        <p>
                            You run a very fair and honest company, which is why I will continue to purchase your daily fixed matches. 
