                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-2 d-none d-sm-block">
                        <img src="/Content/imgWebsite/defFace.jpg" class="img img-rounded img-fluid" alt="customer comment about fixed matches" title="customer comment"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-10">
                        <p>
                            <a class="float-left"><strong>Mario Garvilia</strong></a>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                        </p>
                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                        <p>
                            A genuine service. I’ve been with them for a while now and they have always provided me with nice sure tips that always win. That is very good for me, 
                            cause it gives great morale knowing that every day you have at least one prediction that always wins.
                        </p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-2 d-none d-sm-block">
                        <img src="/Content/imgWebsite/defFace.jpg" class="img img-rounded img-fluid lazy" alt="customer comment about fixed matches" title="customer comment"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-10">
                        <p>
                            <a class="float-left"><strong>Andrea  Carloti</strong></a>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                            <span class="float-right"><i class="text-warning fa fa-star"></i></span>
                        </p>
                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                        <p>
                            Let me wrap this up in 2 words: VERY POWER FULL !. I was referred by a friend and boy am i happy i signed up for this sure fixed matches offer. 
                            This guy offers me a very nice EXTRA INCOME each month.
                        </p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card text-white bg-secondary my-5 text-center">
    <div class="card-body">
        <p class="text-white m-0">
            Passed matches from our daily monthly fixed matches offer
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="table-responsive">
    <table class="table table-bordered table-sm" style="overflow-y:auto;">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th scope="col">Date</th>
            <th scope="col">TotalOdd</th>
            <th scope="col">Match</th>
            <th scope="col">Tip</th>
            <th scope="col">Odd</th>
            <th scope="col">Result</th>
            <th scope="col">Win/Lose</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        @foreach (var tip in Model.MonthlySubscrations)
        {
            <tr>
                <td>@tip.Date</td>
                <td>@String.Format("{0:0.00}",tip.TotalOdd)</td>
                <td>@tip.Match</td>
                <td>@tip.Tip</td>
                <td>@String.Format("{0:0.00}",tip.Odd)</td>
                <td>@tip.Result</td>
                <td>@tip.WinLose</td>
            </tr>
        }
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>




@section scripts {
    <script>
        var list = [];
        $(document).ready(function() {
            $.getJSON("/JsonFiles/MonthlyOffers.json", function(result){
                $.each(result, function(key, value){
                    list.push(value);
                    $(".js-Offers").append(
                        '<div class="col-md-4 mb-5"><div class="card h-100"><div class="card-body">'+
                        '<h2 class="card-title">' + value.NameOffer + '</h2>'+
                        '<p class="card-text">' + value.TextOffer +
                        '</p>' +
                        '<p class="card-text"><b>' + value.PriceOffer +
                        ' euros</b></p>' +
                        '</div></div></div>'
                    );
                });
            });
        });

    </script>

}
